<div class="auth-shell">
  <div class="auth-grid">
    <section class="auth-hero">
      <div class="auth-hero-content">
        <div class="auth-kicker">
          <span class="auth-kicker-dot"></span>
          Designed for deep work, not just checklists
        </div>
        <h1 class="auth-title">Personal Productivity Hub</h1>
        <p class="auth-subtitle">
          Log in to a focused workspace where your tasks, notes, and priorities
          stay in one calm, intentional place. Build momentum one small win at a time.
        </p>

        <div class="auth-pills">
          <div class="auth-pill">
            <span class="auth-pill-dot"></span>
            Capture and clarify your day in seconds
          </div>
          <div class="auth-pill">
            <span class="auth-pill-dot"></span>
            See tasks by energy, not just deadlines
          </div>
          <div class="auth-pill">
            <span class="auth-pill-dot"></span>
            Protect time for deep work blocks
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="auth-stats">
          <div class="auth-stat">
            <div class="auth-stat-label">Daily focus sessions</div>
            <div class="auth-stat-value">+3</div>
          </div>
          <div class="auth-stat">
            <div class="auth-stat-label">Tasks that truly matter</div>
            <div class="auth-stat-value">42%</div>
          </div>
          <div class="auth-stat">
            <div class="auth-stat-label">Average distraction time</div>
            <div class="auth-stat-value">-27%</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="auth-quote">
          <div class="auth-quote-mark">“</div>
          <div>
            <div>
              Once I started planning my day here, my calendar stopped feeling like a
              to‑do list and started feeling like a strategy.
            </div>
            <div class="auth-quote-meta">Built for people who want to ship, not just stay busy.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="auth-form-card">
      <div class="auth-form-header">
        <h2 class="auth-form-title">Welcome back</h2>
        <p class="auth-form-subtitle">Log in to pick up where you left off.</p>
      </div>

      <form method="post" action="/auth/login">
        <div class="auth-field-group">
          <div class="auth-field-label">
            <label for="email">Email</label>
          </div>
          <input id="email" type="email" name="email" autocomplete="email" required />
        </div>

        <div class="auth-field-group">
          <div class="auth-field-label">
            <label for="password">Password</label>
            <span class="auth-field-helper">Keep it private. We keep it encrypted.</span>
          </div>
          <input
            id="password"
            type="password"
            name="password"
            autocomplete="current-password"
            required
          />
        </div>

        <div class="auth-actions">
          <button type="submit">
            Log into your workspace
          </button>
          <div class="auth-secondary-link">
            New here?
            <a href="/auth/signup">Create an account</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </form>

      <div class="auth-badge-row">
        <div class="auth-badge">Built for deep work & realistic planning.</div>
        <div class="auth-badge">Your data stays in your workspace.</div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>
